headline: Federal Realty Investment Trust Reports Second Quarter 2025 Results
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE: FRT) today reported its results for the second quarter ended June 30, 2025. For the three months ended June 30, 2025 and 2024, net income available for common shareholders was $1.78 per diluted share and $1.32 per diluted share, respectively. Operating income for the same periods was $202.7 million and $157.0 million, respectively.
